#. class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "thag1.4:1.1"
msgid "Theragāthā"
msgstr "Verses of the Senior Monks"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thag1.4:2.1"
msgid "Ekakanipāta"
msgstr "The Book of the Ones"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thag1.4:3.1"
msgid "Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "Chapter One"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.4:4.1"
msgid "1.4. Puṇṇattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.4. Puṇṇa (1st)"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc4"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts4"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.4:5.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha,"
msgstr "Associate only with the virtuous,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.4:5.2"
msgid "paṇḍitehatthadassibhi;"
msgstr "the astute ones who see the goal."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.4:5.3"
msgid "Atthaṃ mahantaṃ gambhīraṃ,"
msgstr "The wise ones, diligent and discerning,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.4:5.4"
msgid "duddasaṃ nipuṇaṃ aṇuṃ;"
msgstr "realize the goal"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.4:5.5"
msgid "Dhīrā samadhigacchanti,"
msgstr "so great and profound,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.4:5.6"
msgid "appamattā vicakkhaṇā”ti."
msgstr "hard to see, subtle, and fine."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag1.4:6.1"
msgid ""
"Itthaṃ sudaṃ āyasmā puṇṇo <span class=\"var\" title=\"mantāniputto (s2, s3, "
"pts1-2, mr)\" id=\"note4\">mantāṇiputto</span> thero gāthaṃ abhāsitthāti."
msgstr ""
"It was thus that this verse was recited by the senior venerable Puṇṇa "
"Mantāṇiputta."
